   "body" : "This fixes the deadlock in the `CScheduler` when there are other `serviceQueue`s waiting for the new task to be added to the `taskQueue`, but `schedule` notifies only one of them who processes it and ends. And the other ones get stucked waiting for the new task which doesn't come in at all.\r\n\r\nHard to reproduce, see #6540 for the discussion.\r\n\r\nFixes #6540.",
